abstract: College Basketball Roundup; William Paterson University players forfeit game against Ramapo College, leaving floor shortly before tipoff, in protest of resignation of Paterson coach Jose Rebimbas.
lead_paragraph: The men’s basketball team at William Paterson, a Division III university in Wayne, N.J., was apparently protesting the departure of Coach Jose Rebimbas.

headline.main: William Paterson Forfeits Game After Coach’s Departure
